{"tw": {"2445340": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love n Life: Lucky Teacher", "steam_appid": 2445340, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3216840, 2662040], "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=688 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>69愛愛病毒大流行後，世界陷入了金融危機。你原本是那須的航空專家，卻因為經濟不景氣被炒了魷魚，只能離開大城市，跑到小鎮裡去當老師。不過命運出現了意料之外的轉折，黑暗中也有一絲光明，或許你的桃花……才剛剛綻放？做好小鎮老師的工作，譜寫自己的愛情故事。你將邂逅各式各樣的美少女，並在交往中慢慢了解她們的故事。準備好迎接一段難忘的敘事體驗吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/fa6d1ecdca6fe79fe1a3bd9966e055b0.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=688 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/fa6d1ecdca6fe79fe1a3bd9966e055b0.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/fa6d1ecdca6fe79fe1a3bd9966e055b0.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>美麗的女孩們在Live2d動畫。<br></li><li>有趣的卡通角色，環境，和美麗的城市。<br></li><li>用於房間裝飾的禮物和迷人的服裝。有趣的迷你遊戲。<br></li><li>對話選項會影響好感度。超過35,000個故事文本。<br></li><li>逼真的文字模擬，帶有出色的效果。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/01e3e31c4ac0696d427f84ecaa3a7bd4.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=688 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/01e3e31c4ac0696d427f84ecaa3a7bd4.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/01e3e31c4ac0696d427f84ecaa3a7bd4.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>百合子小姐 💕 一個充滿活力的冒險</strong><br>一個有著奢華背景的學生，她是一個沉迷於遊戲和偶像文化的狂熱愛好者。她充滿活力的個性和滿滿的自信可能會讓你不知所措。她通常會讓你陷入困境，但對於像你這樣經驗豐富的人來說，這些困境可能會成為你的黃金機會。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/634d911e7cfc2f8dabebc7f22f12f557.avif?t=1773974727\" width=555 height=450 /></span><br><br><br><strong>日葵女士 💕 一個意外的相遇</strong><br>當你在家裡輔導她的妹妹(百合子小姐)時，她意外地與你相遇。她優雅的氣場，華麗的藍眼睛，和陽光般的微笑瞬間觸動了你的心靈。在這些輔導課程中，意想不到的事情發生了，你和這位美麗的女士之間建立了深厚的聯繫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/ccdfa8e2c6eb76e69a4abf3833259e98.avif?t=1773974727\" width=555 height=450 /></span><br><br><br><strong>真澄小姐 💕 擁抱新的開始</strong><br>你申請當老師的教育中心主任因為過去的心痛而渴望真愛。在你到來的時候，她看到了一個有潛力修復她心靈創傷的真正英雄。她的經歷會讓你著迷，將你編織成一張感情的網。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/80fbda82333e15fd0fbeb906b09e1229.avif?t=1773974727\" width=555 height=450 /></span><br><br><br><strong>心怡 💕 一個溫馨的相遇</strong><br>一個溫柔勤奮的中國留學生。她舉止安靜，可能會給建立親密關係帶來挑戰，但當你了解她內心時，你會發現她有美好的個性。你理想的約會地點是一個舒適的咖啡館，在那裡你們可以分享溫馨的時刻。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/2a332834b542c0e28f64242a8934cc47.avif?t=1773974727\" width=555 height=450 /></span>", "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/143f0f3b9883594a9089e91d663b1511.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.poster.avif?t=1773974727\" width=688 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.webm?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445340/extras/77862a2450bfd8050b7b732ff0ae4281.mp4?t=1773974727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>69愛愛病毒大流行後，世界陷入了金融危機。你原本是那須的航空專家，卻因為經濟不景氣被炒了魷魚，只能離開大城市，跑到小鎮裡去當老師。不過命運出現了意料之外的轉折，黑暗中也有一絲光明，或許你的桃花……才剛剛綻放？做好小鎮老師的工作，譜寫自己的愛情故事。你將邂逅各式各樣的美少女，並在交往中慢慢了解她們的故事。準備好迎接一段難忘的敘事體驗吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" au